{"tid":991770,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"撻完車但㗎車唔郁","createTime":"2019-01-22T15:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T08:05:20.000Z","uid":49716,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d7118d6ebbac1f61187e9b61dcbfb533d49f4882","tid":991770,"uid":49716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"㗎車係98年Mazda 323 ，屋企人用開，但一直少用。今年考左牌，所以拎黎用住先。<br />\n<br />\n但架車撻著左之後唔可以即刻行，要成個字先會郁。佢轉數一撻會keep住千幾轉慢慢落返去，溫度都要啲時間先升到上去。入d波踏行油踏到手3，4000轉都唔郁，可能淨係會行前少少咁。但入後波又無事。架車行順左之後就咩事都無，行得好順。但一耐無著車又會變返咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係唔係要成個波箱換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651d329195beef65c9a9809ab6a5c1c55bc3bf01","tid":991770,"uid":81686,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:36:41.000Z","msg":"人要惡過車<br />\n你份人好林善?"},{"pid":"ee955621ec55e4f8ed3551ea252d492efe2bb74a","tid":991770,"uid":65436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:37:34.000Z","msg":"有冇著咩燈"},{"pid":"de2e7406d46f21c1ccd5d4125b583f7e0e764e43","tid":991770,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:38:45.000Z","msg":"舊車最好暖下車"},{"pid":"a802eed7b2949b831b7b3f6b053dc1c96365b324","tid":991770,"uid":37297,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:39:18.000Z","msg":"有冇鬆手掣..."},{"pid":"c45759fba56ea5cd94d42948eada601df1b34404","tid":991770,"uid":28818,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好危險<br />\n搵次你以為比大油佢都唔郁佢一野彈出去你都仆街"},{"pid":"7ae38dea629b7e116d638ecd756c77632d312274","tid":991770,"uid":49716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee955621ec55e4f8ed3551ea252d492efe2bb74a","tid":991770,"uid":65436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15:37:34.000Z","msg":"有冇著咩燈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T15: